snippet.title: SONIC PROJECT S Final Trailer
snippet.description:
With tons of songs from tons of fans, challenging gameplay and a low price of FREE, SONIC PROJECT S is looking to rock your world on July 28th at SAGE 2018! 

Trailer music from LOGI 
at https://logi.bandcamp.com/
